==English==
===Noun===
# An underground warrior in, from, or sympathetic to an occupied country with inferior resources who is dedicated to inflicting maximum damage at minimum cost to a weak strategic position of the occupier or their allied suporter.  Especially a refugee, or his ally, so desperate and dedicated to defending a homeland as to engage in a suicide attack.  
# One who employs terror as a political weapon.  Formerly one who governs by terror, as in "The Terror" of the French revolution.

